# Visualization Components

The ECG monitoring system includes JavaScript-based visualization for displaying and analyzing ECG data:

## ECG Graph Visualization

- **Main Visualization**: [web/public/js/ecg-visualization.js](mdc:web/public/js/ecg-visualization.js)
  - Uses Chart.js library for rendering ECG signals
  - Supports real-time data plotting and historical data viewing

- **Interactive Features**:
  - Zoom and pan capabilities for detailed analysis
  - Wave identification (P, Q, R, S, T)
  - Measurement tools for intervals and amplitudes

## User Interface Components

- **Main Styles**: [web/public/css/main.css](mdc:web/public/css/main.css)
  - Responsive design for various device sizes
  - Modern UI components for medical data display

- **Diagnostic Interface**: [web/public/css/diagnostic.css](mdc:web/public/css/diagnostic.css)
  - Specialized styling for diagnostic views
  - Printable report formats

## Pages

- **Configuration Page**: [web/pages/configuration.php](mdc:web/pages/configuration.php)
  - Patient and acquisition setup interface
  - Form for entering patient information securely

- **Diagnostic Page**: [web/pages/diagnostic.php](mdc:web/pages/diagnostic.php)
  - Professional medical interface for analysis
  - Tools for entering diagnostic findings and measurements

